{"tid":2035891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男商人提私人檢控　擬控郭榮鏗 14 項公職人員行為失當罪　陳文慧任代表律師","createTime":"2020-05-26T07:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T04:31:03.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9323f577a3b5dce8d3473d02b9dccebade662c83","tid":2035891,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QLXMGvg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQLXMGvg.png&h=b74ac943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會內務委員會歷時半年未能選出主席風波，令主持會議的公民黨郭榮鏗遭建制派質疑其濫權拖延等。一名中年男商人今由大律師陳文慧和律師陳永良代表，於沙田裁判法院提出私人檢控，擬檢控郭榮鏗「公職人員行為失當」罪。陳永良於庭外表示，打算檢控郭共14項公職人員行為失當罪，指郭由去年 10 月至今年 4 月，主持內務委員會選主席期間涉 14 次有所拖延，導致很多法案未能提上大會表決，影響民生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%94%B7%E5%95%86%E4%BA%BA%E6%8F%90%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7-%E6%93%AC%E6%8E%A7%E9%83%AD%E6%A6%AE%E9%8F%97-14-%E9%A0%85%E5%85%AC%E8%81%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%E5%A4%B1%E7%95%B6%E7%BD%AA-%E9%99%B3%E6%96%87%E6%85%A7%E4%BB%BB%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%2595%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258F%2590%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2583%25AD%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E9%258F%2597-14-%25E9%25A0%2585%25E5%2585%25AC%25E8%2581%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E7%2595%25B6%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2585%25A7%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%2F&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjYyNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=24258009\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%2595%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258F%2590%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2583